data.description: Welcome To 1105 E Carson Street! This 4 Story Multi Unit Building Is Currently Used As Two Income Producing AirBnbs. Features A Stunning Rooftop Balcony With Incredible Views Of The City, Beautiful Hard Wood Floors, Updated Bathrooms, Open Concept With High Ceilings, Original Woodwork, Pocket Doors And So Much More! Walk Inside From The Rooftop Balcony To A 4th Floor Kitchen & Bar Area, Great For Entertainment. The 2nd, 3rd and 4th Floors Are Currently Used As One Massive Airbnb Unit With The 1st Floor As Its Own Separate Airbnb Unit. 1st Floor Can Also Be Used As A Storefront/Retail With 20 Feet Of Frontage On East Carson Street Where There Is A traffic Count Of Over 12,000 Cars Per Day. Just Steps Away From Many Popular Bars, Restaurants, And Shopping. Property Can Also Be Used As An Owner Occupied Suite On 3rd and 4th Floors While Renting Floors 1 & 2 As Airbnb or To Long Term Tenants. Available Now! Schedule A Tour To See This Incredible Cash Flowing Building!
